.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-diff 1  "diff 0.2.0" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-diff \- Compare two pack versions and report what changed
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp diff\fR [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-type\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-threshold\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK_A\fR> <\fIPACK_B\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compare two pack versions and report what changed
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-type\fR \fI<TYPE>\fR
Diff only one asset type (term, chunk, rule, constraint)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-threshold\fR \fI<THRESHOLD>\fR [default: 20]
Content\-drift percentage threshold for "modified" classification
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK_A\fR>
First pack directory or archive
.TP
<\fIPACK_B\fR>
Second pack directory or archive
.SH VERSION
v0.2.0
